    <div class="main review-item" id="6856132">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6856132/" class="title-link">笔记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6856132"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/tan-mu/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3340912-60.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/tan-mu/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">魏小河</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-08-29"
      class="main-meta">2014-08-29 16:19:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6856132_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  所谓黏性，是指你的创意与观点能让人听懂，能被人记住，并形成持久的影响。当然，我们都希望自己的创意和观点具有粘性，具体怎么破，请看黏性创意的六大原则。  ▎原则一：简单——核心+精炼  第一步，找到核心。你真正想要传达的是什么？只有找到核心，之后的所有努力才有价值...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">19有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            中信出版社2014版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6856132_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6856132_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
